==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underbearer
<hw>Un"der*bear`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
supports or sustains; especially, at a funeral, one of those who bear
the corpse, as distinguished from a <contr>bearer</contr>, or
<contr>pallbearer</contr>, who helps to hold up the pall.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underbelly</ent>⟦br⟧
